_sText:
A fun map originally for Minigames, re-make for Minigames.

Disclaimer: I am not the author of mg_pushcircle_rfix2

This map consist of 13 musics, all fit nicely into the gameplay. All song credits goes to their rightful newgrounds.com authors.

4 Ramps will toggle open after 1.5 minute.

Airaccelerate has been changed to 500 in order to have the maximum fun. On top of this, svenablebunnyhopping, svenableboost has been set to true.

Every round, instead on the normal pushcircle, you will be given a weapon at random.

Weapon List:
-M4A1
-AK47
-MAC10
-TMP
-UMP45
-M3
-XM1014
-Dual Elites
-M249
-Famas
-Galil
-SG552
-Scout
-MP5
-AUG
-P90

Question/Comments/Bug? Leave them here! Please Rate and explain, thank you very much!
